paint

public void paint(Canvas canvas,
                  Paint paint,
                  float bearing,
                  Collection<? extends POIModel> pois)
Paints the radar on screen. Performs rotations to keep it oriented with the device rotation and draws all visible POIs on screen in the radar.

Parameters:
canvas - The canvas where to paint the radar
paint - The paint object used
bearing - The bearing to rotate and show on screen
pois - The collection of pois to draw on the radar
